Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class 7 Special Hazard Organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.62,0:00:08.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has been thrown\N into chaos because of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.84,0:00:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Including your plan\Nto liberate Dorssia?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was once asked by Captain Cain to secretly\Ninvestigate you since you're a formal royal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rejoice, H-neun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.31,0:00:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}X-eins' flesh will soon\Nbelong to my comrade.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.44,0:00:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Bastard!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.99,0:00:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I think it's time for\Na gun salute, don't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was that... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is. It was Captain\NCain who killed H-neun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avenge H-neun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.80,0:00:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to avenge my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too much for them!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.64,0:01:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make it, don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.35,0:01:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Carmilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Unit 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.25,0:01:23.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rukino's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They say that Unit 4's back!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hear Tokishima's with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto? He's back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we made it\Nback just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.88,0:01:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. All that's left is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this thing really took a beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not surprising,\Nafter fighting a Valvrave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.68,0:01:46.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a survivor here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Send some people over!\NLet's get the pilot out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to create a country where\Nhumans and Kamitsuki can live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that,\Nwe need territory, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's going to take more than\Nland to make that work, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.13,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do right now is get things\Nunderway one step at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:42.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, it's just not possible!\NNot with just four Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.93,0:03:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Module 77 is being guarded by\N40,000 Allied Forces soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.14,0:03:52.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get swept up in the excitement.\NThink it through carefully, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want a place where\NI can belong, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.61,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf is already\Ninfiltrating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A simultaneous attack\Nfrom inside and outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.20,0:04:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Between us and L-elf,\Nthis plan will work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can trust you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.70,0:04:14.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can count on me. I'll get\Nour home back no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:27.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Switching places with an injured soldier\Nto infiltrate an enemy position.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same gambit you used\Nin the New Guinea Conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't the one\Nwho gave me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.11,0:04:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I had, would you\Nhave believed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.41,0:04:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer bear you any ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.33,0:04:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, you are\N an enemy of the state.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, my beloved homeland is being
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.90,0:04:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,gnawed away at in secret by monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And so, L-elf, I want you to\Nassist us with our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mission objectives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The elimination of Captain Cain\Nand all parties related to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our interests are aligned, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby sanction Special Forces\NLieutenant L-elf's return to duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blitzendegen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:25.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, how much do you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.66,0:05:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I asked Professor\NKibukawa about the Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our memories will fade away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.19,0:05:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And in the end, we...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's fine! I can still\Nremember everything just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.67,0:05:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.05,0:05:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put on a tough\Nact, not to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your "We'll win for sure" speech back there\Nwas also to put everyone at ease, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.05,0:05:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you have to\Nput on a brave face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For others and for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.18,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us gives up\N to the bitter end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I don't give up,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.01,0:06:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}will he also see how I feel?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:13.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what the outcome will be,\Nbut if we give up, it'll never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.66,0:06:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna borrow this, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You always slack off when it comes\Nto defense, Yamada. You need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.97,0:06:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't a problem! I punch them\Nbefore they can punch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And for the last time...\Nit's "Thunder," damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.44,0:06:39.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put some effort into defense, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.27,0:06:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get off my case, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're talking tens of\Nthousands of enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if even the Valvraves\Ncan win against that many, so—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.82,0:06:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me!\NI'm coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I got new\Nfriends now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:06.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Um... It's okay, Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eat me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.35,0:07:21.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira! I shouldn't\Nhave said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.31,0:07:22.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In regards to the disposal of the Kamitsuki,\Nthe Council supports your plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am of the opinion that surprise attacks\Nshould be as sensational as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to your plan, the public has\Ndirected their rage at those students.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.00,0:07:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plu, this will make it easier\Nto retrieve your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.39,0:07:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We never would have known\N of those artificial Magiuses
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.23,0:07:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you had not informed us\N of the Valvrave Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:07:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have our gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have mine as well, Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.43,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,\NYou rescued me when I was lost and adrift.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.61,0:08:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Miss Sashinami, Professor.\NI'm supposed to be the adult here, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.25,0:08:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that,\Njust get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.62,0:08:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's asking for permission to land.\NWhat do you want us to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's come for revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.38,0:08:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After what we did,\Ncan you blame him?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.21,0:08:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Turn him away, Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But without the Valvraves\Nto protect us, we're as good as—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to do something, Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the prime minister, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.27,0:08:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.06,0:08:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- I knew it, he really is a monster!\N- Why's he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a ship for humans, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:53.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.28,0:08:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving us all\Nfrom the Allied Forces earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That said, please restrict\Nyourself to this hangar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As prime minister, I can't let you in,\Nnot when I can't be certain you are not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.76,0:09:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have lied to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.48,0:09:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd been honest with you,\Neven if it meant getting hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,maybe we could've found a way\Nto work through this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.49,0:09:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With that in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.68,0:09:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at least
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,going to expose the lies\N of the world to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.16,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Expose the lies?\NOf the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get humans at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:49.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That human was sitting\Nin here for ages, crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saying, "I'm sorry,\NHaruto. I'm sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes you have to\Nput on a brave face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.25,0:10:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we catch a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.07,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens of the world!\NThis is a historic day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.66,0:11:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because on this day, our two countries, which could\Nnot be said to have ever been on friendly terms,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.83,0:11:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have joined together in common cause\Nto exterminate the shared enemy of all mankind!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.21,0:11:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The nerve of him, making us\Nout to be the bad guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's because the key to making people\Nget along is to have a common enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a good idea\Nto let them go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:23.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We decided to trust them and wait, didn't we?\NThey said that if we went, we'd only get in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:24.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be back.\NThey'll be back, count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Four Valvraves have\Nappeared on my scope!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, they've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Harakiri Blade complete.\NLet's move in to engage them up close.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed according to plan. Deliver Unit 6\Nto satellite Nice 052 by 1950 hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:57.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're here to act as her shield\Nand cut a path through these guys!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inuzuka-senpai, I'm gonna\Nneed your help on this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.11,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're falling back?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:13:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hit and away...\NThey're biding their time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They know our\Nweakness all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Ardor Grips seem to\Nbe doing the trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:20.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're letting us fight without worrying\Nas much about heat management, but still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Deploying in depth defense\Nformation per your orders, Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for Valvrave thermal runaway!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.47,0:13:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This plan of theirs is\Nreckless beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They can't possibly break\Nthrough with just four units.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.02,0:13:31.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose not.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.81,0:13:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Million to one shots do happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.87,0:13:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I want to dispatch Unit 1 personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.36,0:13:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Message from A-drei's Kirschbaum.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He says they are leaving to assist\Nin the defense of Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.29,0:13:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's working. Inform the escort ships\Nin the front and at the harbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three Valvraves are breaching\N#8 defensive perimeter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.13,0:14:00.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Kirschbaum squadron on its way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! Be careful!\NYou are leaking Runes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:20.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What? But I still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.52,0:14:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko... Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.93,0:14:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They have that many\Nhumanoid types?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them to me.\NI'll scatter them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.23,0:15:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The rest of you, go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.73,0:15:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! We have to fight together!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:08.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made a deal to never give up,\Nremember? I'm going with our best bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'll leave you\Nsome Impact Boosters!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Haruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you guys can't use\Nthat attack in quick succession!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.59,0:15:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:30.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A second line?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.15,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave Green is disengaging!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:50.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It has withdrawn\Nat attack speed 14!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this was too big\Na risk after all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.92,0:16:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll enter the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:13.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep going in that direction, and it will\Ntake us to the heart of Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our analysis has determined that they are
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.83,0:16:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,military weapons artificially created\N by the leaders of Old JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.11,0:16:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}There was likely a spirit of patriotism in\Nthe environment that gave rise to such monsters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}But make no mistake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.37,0:16:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}We must place the love of humanity\Nas a whole above the love of any one state!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Our scientific ability progressed too far\Nand created monsters like them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't Haruto and the others there yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.68,0:16:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They aren't showing anything\Nabout the battle on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}They can only be described as a threat...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.48,0:17:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to forget.\NI don't want to forget, but I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm going to fight anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.58,0:17:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because if we run and hide,\Nthere's no future for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice 052!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm latched on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.76,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:30.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:39.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about that, just concentrate!\NNobody but you can do this job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.24,0:18:40.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, keep Akira\Nsafe, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.47,0:19:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're good!\NI'm having a blast!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.69,0:19:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't regret becoming\Na Kamitsuki, not one damn bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:20.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get my revenge\Nand keep my friends safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-chan! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.67,0:19:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even ARUS Splicers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.18,0:19:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your ass is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're done here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hacking successful!\NI did it! I did it, Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.17,0:20:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada? Y-Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! Yamada!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you...\NYou pulled it off, huh? Good deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:37.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,See ya around, Akira.\NMy buddy Nobu gets lonely, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put some effort into defense, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you were right about that, Otamaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.68,0:21:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.09,0:21:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now they'll see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The wound, it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!\NDon't show this!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?! Hurry,\Nhave them cut the transmission!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.65,0:22:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use! The communications\Nsatellite has been hacked!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't control it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.24,0:22:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what the Valvraves were doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.00,0:22:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defend this transmission with my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.17,0:22:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spread! Spread!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.27,0:22:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth of the world\Nhas been exposed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.37,0:24:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 24.\N"Liberation Towards Tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.46,0:24:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator... The system that\Nwill expose the truth of the world.